locality: Yemen, gov. Al-Mahra, Northern Fartak Mts., dissected table-land W. below J. Karmoum.
Plants of Yemen. Hadhramout, Wadi Hajar, between As Sadara and Mir Mintaq.

Vicinity of village of Rizui (Tibetan name = Riza); on steep S- to W-facing slopes above village along trail to oak and pine forest (matsutake harvest site); steep rocky S- to W-facing slopes along trail above village, scrub vegetation, low shrubs with scattered Platycladus; common forage grass, mostly not yet flowering
